{"tid":1005382,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"懷舊是懷舊香港　不是中國　香港人的國家是香港　不是中國","createTime":"2019-02-02T07:35:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T14:17:11.000Z","uid":47714,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"93449ee6fb99b2aa842669a00004453c10b6b7d9","tid":1005382,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T07:35:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/1073468132998578177\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F1073468132998578177&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2Wg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=85509432\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F1073468132998578177&h=22c947f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/1073468132998578177</a><br />\n<br />\n我們社會，懷舊是懷舊香港，不是懷舊中國，熱愛本土不是喜愛中國，本地蛋不是中國蛋，我們對 made in Hong Kong 充滿情懷時 made in China 是另一種東西。哪裡是香港人的國家其實非常明顯，絕不是中國。我們香港人，香港利益就是我們國家利益，中國利益是敵國利益，中國是香港敵國，兩者利益是衝突的。"},{"pid":"b472f26879f3e7022ee3e11db22f4b5e3dea87a8","tid":1005382,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93449ee6fb99b2aa842669a00004453c10b6b7d9","tid":1005382,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T07:35:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/1073468132998578177\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F1073468132998578177&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2Wg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=85509432\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F1073468132998578177&h=22c947f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/1073468132998578177</a><br />\n<br />\n我們社會，懷舊是懷舊香港，不是懷舊中國，熱愛本土不是喜愛中國，本地蛋不是中國蛋，我們對 made in Hong Kong 充滿情懷時 made in China 是另一種東西。哪裡是香港人的國家其實非常明顯，絕不是中國。我們香港人，香港利益就是我們國家利益，中國利益是敵國利益，中國是香港敵國，兩者利益是衝突的。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T14:17:11.000Z","msg":"連登仔理感情台都唔會理香港"}]}